import { Component } from '@angular/core'; interface FileWithUrl { file: File; url: string; type:string; name:string; } @Component({ selector: 'app-signuppage', templateUrl: './signuppage.component.html', styleUrls: ['./signuppage.component.scss'] }) export class SignuppageComponent { files: any[] = []; onSelect(event: any) { console.log(event); this.files.push(...event.addedFiles); } onRemove(event: any) { console.log(event); this.files.splice(this.files.indexOf(event), 1); } }
